1. *Apsolutno* se slažem sa tvojim stavom. (I absolutely agree with your position.)
2. *Apsolutno* je nepoželjno da to uradite. (It is absolutely undesirable for you to do that.)
3. Ovaj izazov je *apsolutno* nepremostiv. (This challenge is absolutely insurmountable.)
4. Ona je *apsolutno* najbolja u tome. (She is absolutely the best at it.)
5. On je *apsolutno* ustuknuo na pitanje. (He completely shied away from the question.)